<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Under AP, credit is granted for scores of 4 or 5 for a maximum of 4 hours of credit per course upon the recommendation of the department in which the credit is to be given. For a score of 3 a decision on whether to grant credit will be made by the appropriate Hastings College department.  No additional tuition charge is made for the acceptance of AP credit.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.hastings.edu/igsbase/igstemplate.cfm/SRC=DB/SRCN=/GnavID=28/SnavID=149" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

